# Pizza APIS

These APIs are for a pizza restaurant.

## MOCK APIs [/]

### List a pizza detail [GET/menu/{menu_item_id}]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "id": 1,
              "name": "Margherita",
              "description": "Classic pizza with tomato sauce, mozzarella, and basil",
              "price": 12.99,
              "image_url": "https://pizza-restaurant.com/images/margherita.jpg"
            }
        
### Place a new order [POST/order]


+ Request (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "customer_name": "John Doe",
              "customer_email": "johndoe@example.com",
              "items": [
                {
                  "pizza_id": 1,
                  "quantity": 2
                },
                {
                  "pizza_id": 2,
                  "quantity": 1
                }
              ]
            }
            
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "message": "Order successfull placed."
            }
            
### Cancel the order [DELETE/orders/{order_id}]

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {
              "message": "Order 4 has been cancelled."
            }

